9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Bubble | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"In a Tokyo where gravity has broken, a boy and a girl are drawn to each other...<br>\n<br>\nThe story is set in Tokyo, after bubbles that broke the laws of gravity rained down upon the world. Cut off from the outside world, Tokyo has become a playground for a group of young people who have lost their families, acting as a battlefield for parkour team battles as they leap from building to building. Hibiki, a young ace known for his dangerous play style, makes a reckless move one day and plummets into the gravity-bending sea. His life is saved by Uta, a girl with mysterious powers. The pair then hear a unique sound audible only to them. Why did Uta appear before Hibiki? Their encounter leads to a revelation that will change the world.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Netflix)<br>\n<br>\n<i>Note: The anime released on Netflix on April 28, 2022. It screened in theaters on May 13, 2022.</i>"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/anime/149882/bubble"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Bubble"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"In a Tokyo where gravity has broken, a boy and a girl are drawn to each other...<br>\n<br>\nThe story is set in Tokyo, after bubbles that broke the laws of gravity rained down upon the world. Cut off from the outside world, Tokyo has become a playground for a group of young people who have lost their families, acting as a battlefield for parkour team battles as they leap from building to building. Hibiki, a young ace known for his dangerous play style, makes a reckless move one day and plummets into the gravity-bending sea. His life is saved by Uta, a girl with mysterious powers. The pair then hear a unique sound audible only to them. Why did Uta appear before Hibiki? Their encounter leads to a revelation that will change the world.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Netflix)<br>\n<br>\n<i>Note: The anime released on Netflix on April 28, 2022. It screened in theaters on May 13, 2022.</i>"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/anime/149882/bubble"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx142455-5cBnV4rz5ISf.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.tv_show"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Bubble"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"In a Tokyo where gravity has broken, a boy and a girl are drawn to each other...<br>\n<br>\nThe story is set in Tokyo, after bubbles that broke the laws of gravity rained down upon the world. Cut off from the outside world, Tokyo has become a playground for a group of young people who have lost their families, acting as a battlefield for parkour team battles as they leap from building to building. Hibiki, a young ace known for his dangerous play style, makes a reckless move one day and plummets into the gravity-bending sea. His life is saved by Uta, a girl with mysterious powers. The pair then hear a unique sound audible only to them. Why did Uta appear before Hibiki? Their encounter leads to a revelation that will change the world.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Netflix)<br>\n<br>\n<i>Note: The anime released on Netflix on April 28, 2022. It screened in theaters on May 13, 2022.</i>"}],"$L12","$L13","$L14"],"error":null,"digest":"$undefined"}
